



Create a build file like this:

<?xml version="1.0"?>

<project name="test" default="main">
	<taskdef name="freemarkerValidator" classname="de.neuland.tools.ant.FreemarkerValidatorTask"/>

	<target name="main">
		<freemarkerValidator verbose="true">
			<fileset dir="web/webroot/WEB-INF/views">
				<include name="**/*.ftl"/>
			</fileset>
		</freemarkerValidator>
	</target>

</project>


You will need freemarker-validation-task.jar and the current freemarker.jar in your Classpath to make things work.
